---
title: Teriyaki Beef Bowls with Edamame Rice and Garlicky Broccoli
description: Sweet and savoury, simple and satisfying: teriyaki is a family flavour favourite for good reason. Plus, we snuck some edamame in the rice to add an extra plant-based protein punch!
